text: Franeker () is a city in the province of Friesland, the Netherlands. It is the capital of the municipality of Waadhoeke. As of 1 January 2014, 12,781 people lived there. == Other websites == * Category:21st-century disestablishments in the Netherlands Category:Cities in Friesland Category:Former municipalities of Friesland Category:Waadhoeke
